{
  "title": "ISic003390. Attic decree",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">Δεινίας</span>  <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">Κηφ[ισο]δότου</span></span> Βουτάδης</span>  <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>θεσμοθετήσας ἐπὶ <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">Φειδοστράτου</span></span>  <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἄρχοντος ἀνέθηκεν <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[ἡ βουλή] ὁ δῆμος </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Giorgia Capra</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Δεινίας Κηφισοδότου Βουτάδης\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Δεινίας\">ΔΕΙΝΙΑΣ</span><span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"patronym\" data-text=\"Κηφισοδότου\">ΚΗΦ[...]ΔΟΤΟΥ</span></span>ΒΟΥΤΑΔΗΣ</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΘΕΣΜΟΘΕΤΗΣΑΣΕΠΙ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Φειδοστράτου\">ΦΕΙΔΟΣΤΡΑΤΟΥ</span></span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΑΡΧΟΝΤΟΣΑΝΕΘΗΚΕΝ<br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[......]ΟΔΗΜΟΣ</span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of IG</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>Deinias son of Kephisodotos of Boutadai, who was thesmothete when Pheidostratos was archon, dedicated this. (In crown, on the left) The Council. (In crown, on the right) The People.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\" https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1030-5679\">Giorgia Capra</a></p>  <p>Deinias figlio di Kephisodotos di Boutadai, che era tesmoteta durante l'arcontato di Pheidostratos, dedicò questo. (In corona, a sinistra) Il consiglio. (In corona, a destra) Il popolo.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>The inscription appears already in the museum inventory of 1885, described as 'prov. incerta', and was previously observed in the earlier version of the museum by Julius Schubring in the 1860s. There is no record of how it came to be in Sicily, and as Manganaro obserfves, it most likely arrived as ballast stone in a ship (at some date prior to c.1860).</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> 02/03(2).3.1.2855 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000420</a>  </li><li> 02/03(3).4.1.99 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000413</a>  </li><li> Schubring 1861-1867 672 no. 7, tab. no.7 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001601</a></li><li> Libertini 1929 121 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001872</a>  </li><li> Manganaro 1965 205 tav. LXXV.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001841</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1    Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
  "divs": [
